title: How to Change Your Identity - TAKE ACTION PT. 1

description:
This is episode #1 of a three part series on my secrets to taking action. In this episode, I will teach you how to change the subconscious identity that you have of yourself so that you can stop self-sabotaging and finally get moving in the right direction!
